<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.8.10">
<l>vaṇṭamar cāral māliruñ cōlai māmaṇi vaṇṇarai vaṇaṅkum</l>
<l>toṇṭaraip paravuñ cuṭaroḷi neṭuvēl cūḻvaya lālinaṉ ṉāṭaṉ</l>
<l>kaṇṭalnal vēli maṅkaiyar talaivaṉ kaliyaṉvā yoliceyta paṉuval</l>
<l>koṇṭivai pāṭun tavamuṭai yārka ḷāḷvarik kuraikaṭa lulakē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have merit who sing these, having obtained the text</l>
<l rend="indent">created by poems of Kaliyaṉ, his tall spear of rayed light,</l>
<l>Lord of the good country of Āli surrounded by fields,</l>
<l rend="indent">leader of those of Maṅkai with fine screw pine hedges,</l>
<l>Who praise the devotees who worship</l>
<l rend="indent">the dark jewel-hued one of Māliruñcōlai</l>
<l>With bees resting on the slopes, they will rule this world</l>
<l rend="indent">[encircled by] the roaring sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
